name: www.sealplace.com
overview:
solves the problem of managing the private important paperwork. just snap a photo of your document and upload it to www.sealplace.com (either by sending it thru the email interface, the iphone or android app or the classic web interface). with the help of advance OCR processing of the uploaded images you can find again the documents without big overhead while capturing them. it does not matter, if you capture invoices (to ensure you have them available when claiming warranty), important documents (like passport etc. to be on the safe side while traveling), or images of precious items in case of loss.

in addition to ease of use - the solutions offers high secured storage of the uploaded items.
